headline: 3 Dividend Stocks Beating the S&P in 2025
summary: Enthusiasm for AI stocks has benefited shares of IBM and Seagate so far in 2025.  AT&T says that passage of the One Big, Beautiful Bill has presented a growth opportunity.  Investors appreciate the strong free cash flow generated by IBM, Seagate, and AT&T.
